entry.title: Royal Family Will Unite to Accompany Queen's Coffin Through London
entry.content: The royal family will unite in procession to move Queen Elizabeth II’s coffin from Buckingham Palace to Westminster Hall in London, where it will lie in state for four days before her official funeral.

entry.title: China Evergrande's Soccer Empire Runs Into Trouble
entry.content: China Evergrande’s property business, built with billions of dollars in borrowed money, has had a humiliating comedown. Its formerly brand-burnishing soccer empire is going through one, too.
